NPM Modules dependencies:
- nconf (https://github.com/flatiron/nconf)
- everyauth

Infrastructure dependencies:
- ActiveMQ bus (or any other STOMP compliant bus, like HornetQ, RabbitMQ, ecc....)
- MongoDB (users, rooms storage, ecc...)


Before start, install all npm packages with these commands:
npm install nconf
npm install everyauth@git://github.com/bnoguchi/everyauth.git#express3

